125
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:15,519
Jak pozdě a jak brzy?

126
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:39,279
Nekoukej jak bubák.

127
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,139
Jak mám koukat?

128
00:09:41,679 --> 00:09:43,639
Nejradši bych tam ani nejela,

129
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:45,879
ale to nemohu našim udělat.

130
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,560
Vrátím se brzy!

131
00:09:48,799 --> 00:09:49,319
Opravdu!

132
00:09:50,759 --> 00:09:52,279
Jak brzy se vrátíš?

133
00:09:52,679 --> 00:09:54,000
Po novém roce.

134
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:55,279
Až odpálí ohňostroj,

135
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:57,240
